high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the table near the sofa
Grab the blue credit card that is on the table
Walk to the window that's behind the sofa
Place the credit card behind the blinds onto the window
anns.task_desc: Sticking a credit card on a window

high_descs: Go to the coffee table in the center of the room.
Pick up the blue credit card sitting on the coffee table.
Take the card to the window.
Place the card in the window just behind the blinds.
anns.task_desc: Take the credit card from the coffee table, put it behind the blinds on the window.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the trash can then turn left and walk halfway across the room, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Take the credit card off the edge of the table.
Turn to the left and walk past the couch, then turn left and walk to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: To use the light to see the credit card.
